Invocation Name: sound bath
des: This sound bath will help you focus or sleep in no time! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Sound Bath,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
